queries.text:
SELECT
  user.id, user.mail, user.password, user.first_name, user.last_name, user.age, user.sex, user.orientation, user.country, user.city, user.bio, user.suspended,
  age_gap.user_id, age_gap.min_age, age_gap.max_age,
  fame_rating_gap.user_id, fame_rating_gap.min_fame_rating, fame_rating_gap.max_fame_rating,
  last_position.user_id, last_position.lattitude, last_position.longitude
FROM
  user
  INNER JOIN age_gap ON user.id = age_gap.user_id
  INNER JOIN fame_rating_gap ON user.id = fame_rating_gap.user_id
  INNER JOIN last_position ON user.id = last_position.user_id
WHERE
  user.mail = ? AND user.password = ?
queries.name: GetUserFull
